00:21:28,570 --> 00:21:31,130
in the locker room.

340
00:21:31,206 --> 00:21:35,336
But she's not the only one. I hate P.E.

341
00:21:35,410 --> 00:21:37,241
Well, did you tell your teacher?

342
00:21:37,312 --> 00:21:39,075
He knows.

343
00:21:41,249 --> 00:21:43,513
Stacey, I wish I didn't
have to ask you this...

344
00:21:43,585 --> 00:21:49,182
but do you ever wish Jasmine, or any of
the other kids who were mean to you, harm?

345
00:21:49,257 --> 00:21:52,852
Harm? Like-

346
00:21:54,429 --> 00:21:57,262
You think I made
that video, and that it was-

