I may have thought about revenge, but...

348
00:22:02,637 --> 00:22:04,696
I don't want them to die.

349
00:22:06,241 --> 00:22:08,539
She's telling the truth.
She doesn't want to harm anyone.

350
00:22:10,679 --> 00:22:13,443
Please don't tell Jasmine I told on her.

351
00:22:13,515 --> 00:22:15,346
Oh, sweetie, uh-

352
00:22:15,417 --> 00:22:17,510
Maybe she is the one who made the video...

353
00:22:17,586 --> 00:22:20,885
and all this is her fantasy revenge.

354
00:22:20,956 --> 00:22:22,617
Uh, who's the P.E. teacher?

355
00:22:22,691 --> 00:22:24,522
- Why?
- It's not you, is it?

356
00:22:24,593 --> 00:22:27,824
Yeah, but I would never
turn a blind eye to bullying if I saw it.

357
00:22:27,896 --> 00:22:30,330
Did you know that these kids
were picking on Stacey?

358
00:22:30,399 --> 00:22:32,993
Well, I could see
she wasn't the most popular.

359
00:22:33,068 --> 00:22:37,528
- Is Jasmine popular?
- Yeah, I'd say so. Very, actually.

360
00:22:37,606 --> 00:22:40,473
It's always the popular ones
who think they can get away with murder.

361
