463
00:29:48,803 --> 00:29:50,794
How do you do?

464
00:29:51,906 --> 00:29:53,999
I see you two already know each other.

465
00:29:54,075 --> 00:29:56,600
Well, any-
any friend of Terry's is a friend of mine.

466
00:29:56,678 --> 00:29:59,613
So, pleasantries out of the way.

467
00:29:59,681 --> 00:30:01,649
