469
00:30:06,488 --> 00:30:08,683
I gave you my word. Man to man.

470
00:30:08,756 --> 00:30:10,417
See, now, that's why I'm here.

471
00:30:10,492 --> 00:30:13,359
- Yes or no questions, they only go so far.
- Uh-huh?

472
00:30:13,428 --> 00:30:17,592
So... how flawless is the merchandise?

473
00:30:17,665 --> 00:30:20,657
The currency is perfect.

474
00:30:22,237 --> 00:30:23,966
